AT.name: Meine Tierarztpraxis 3D - Einsatz auf dem Land
AT.description: Viele süße Tiere brauchen deine Hilfe! Baue deine eigene Landpraxis auf und errichte wunderschöne Stallungen. Fahre zu Außeneinsätzen und untersuche die Tiere vor Ort. Besonders kranke Tiere kannst du bei dir aufnehmen und pﬂegen. - Untersuche und behandle Rehe, Lämmer, Hunde, Katzen, Kaninchen, Papageien und Pferde – mit tollem 3D-Effekt. - Zeige dein Talent beim Verband anlegen, Spritze geben, Einsalben und vielem mehr. - Erkunde die Reitstrecke im Wald mit der realistischen Bewegungssteuerung. - Gehe zum Einkaufen in die Stadt und erweitere deine Tierarztpraxis. - Sammle Spielmünzen und tausche sie in Spielwährung um. - 3D-Foto-Feature: Mache ein echtes 3D-Foto von dir und verwende es im Spiel!

BG.name: My Vet Practice 3D - In the Country
BG.description: Start your own vet practice in the countryside – in fantastic 3D! Build beautiful pens and stables for many different kinds of animals. You decide which animals to treat or to go out on house visits and examine the animals on the scene. Really sick animals can be admitted for in- patient care and healed in your animal hospital. - Exciting pet care and building fun in real 3D! - Care for animals like deer, lambs, dogs, cats, bunnies, parakeets and horses. - Enjoy examinations and treatments with fantastic 3D effects: magnifying glass, thermometer, ultrasound scan, syringe, bandage, tweezers and many more. - Innovative 3D-Photo-Feature: Take real 3D pictures of yourself with the Nintendo 3DS™ Camera and use them in the game – now you are a veterinarian for real! - Use the gyroscope controls of your Nintendo 3DS™ and explore the ride out route with your own horse. - Visit the stores in the city or explore and upgrade your own vet practice. - Collect Play Coins to change them into ingame currency.

BE.name: Ma clinique à la campagne 3D
BE.description: Tant d’animaux mignons ont besoin de ton aide ! Construis ton propre cabinet vétérinaire à la campagne et agrandis-le avec de superbes bâtiments. Rends-toi sur le terrain et examine les animaux sur place. Tu peux aussi héberger les animaux très malades et les soigner chez toi. - Examine et apporte tes soins aux biches, agneaux, chiens, chats, lapins, perroquets et chevaux – avec de fantastiques effets 3D. - Montre tes talents : pose des pansements, donne des piqûres, applique du baume et bien plus. - Pars à la découverte du parcours équestre en forêt grâce à l’accéléromètre réaliste. - Va faire tes courses en ville et agrandis ton cabinet vétérinaire. - Collectionne les pièces de jeu Nintendo 3DS™ et échange-les contre de la monnaie de jeu. - Fonction de photo 3D révolutionnaire : fais une vraie photo 3D de toi et utilise-la dans le jeu !

IT.name: La mia clinica veterinaria 3D – Medici in campagna
IT.description: Molti deliziosi animali hanno bisogno del tuo aiuto! Crea il tuo ambulatorio veterinario rurale e costruisci stupende stalle. Recati sul posto e visita gli animali in loco. Può accogliere e curare soprattutto animali ammalati. - Visita e cura caprioli, agnelli, cani, gatti, conigli, pappagalli e cavalli – con meraviglioso effetto 3D. - Mostra il tuo talento nell’eseguire fasciature, fare punture, applicare unguenti e molto altro. - Perlustra la pista equestre nel bosco con il realistico controllo dei movimenti. - Vai a fare acquisti in città e amplia il tuo ambulatorio veterinario. - Collezioni monete di gioco Nintendo 3DS e convertili in valuta da gioco. - Rivoluzionaria Foto-Feature tridimensionale: scattati una vera foto 3D e usala nel gioco!

Really sick animals can be admitted for in- patient care and healed in your animal hospital. - Exciting pet care and building fun in real 3D! - Care for animals like deer, lambs, dogs, cats, bunnies, parakeets and horses. - Enjoy examinations and treatments with fantastic 3D effects: magnifying glass, thermometer, ultrasound scan, syringe, bandage, tweezers and many more. - Innovative 3D-Photo-Feature: Take real 3D pictures of yourself with the Nintendo 3DS™ Camera and use them in the game – now you are a veterinarian for real! - Use the gyroscope controls of your Nintendo 3DS™ and explore the ride out route with your own horse. - Visit the stores in the city or explore and upgrade your own vet practice. - Collect Play Coins to change them into ingame currency.
